{"type":"question","id":2228,"title":"[经略新闻话题]  习的自信，是因为掌握了宇宙真理吗？","uid":798,"topics":[698,847],"contents":"<blockquote><b>马克思主义，走来了</b><br>\n <br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.redd.it/rh3angoxv3i21.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><a href=\"https://i.redd.it/rh3angoxv3i21.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.redd.it/rh3angoxv3i21.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.redd.it/rh3angoxv3i21.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n@AlatukiDxc：<br>\n今天有人跟我说天朝全国上下弥漫着一股自信的味道，有些领域也确实搞的蛮成功的；<br>\n<br>\n我说那不叫自信，自信是你说什么都无所谓，我闷声发大财，让你那些唱衰论不攻自破；<br>\n<br>\n现在是你说什么都有所谓的时代，所以那只能叫宣传。</blockquote><br>\nhttps://www.reddit.com/r/4832/comments/atgir1/","date":"2019-02-22","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}